***************
Command *Move*
***************

Documentation for the Move command in */cmds/wiz/Move.c*.

Command
=======

USAGE::

	 Move <object> <object>

 This command will move the first object into the second one,
 both objects must be present in your environment.

 Move barney safe

   This will put barney into the safe.
